init_text:
Once upon a time there was an old mother pig who had one hundred little pigs and not enough food to feed them. So when they were old enough, she sent them out into the world to seek their fortunes. You know the story about the first three little pigs. This is a story about the 92nd little pig.

The 92nd little pig built a house out of depleted uranium. And the wolf was like, "dude."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The 92nd little pig said, "I don't think so."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I'm not going to help you.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He was just about to turn on the TV when he heard a knock at the door.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I'm just here to say thank you." said the wolf.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Because I was able to go to the bathroom in the bushes, and I didn't have to go in your house."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I was so busy trying to get into your house that I didn't see the box.
